# DNS Setup:
===
Setup a domain like: beyondcloud.online

Base domain: gcp.beyondcloud.online
Cluster name: venky
Full cluster: venky.gcp.beyondcloud.online

Customize the name of the cluster @install-config.yaml file the only way to change it.

gcloud dns managed-zones create ocp-zone \
  --dns-name="gcp.beyondcloud.online." \
  --description="OpenShift GCP DNS zone" \
  --visibility="public"

gcloud dns managed-zones describe ocp-zone \
  --format="value(nameServers)"

dig NS gcp.beyondcloud.online

